Products.RichDescription:
Pureharvest Aussie Dream original with added organic calcium is based on a traditional oriental food that is made from certified organic brown rice. Many people cannot consume dairy milk because of the lactose it contains, as lactose can often lead to allergic reactions and discomfort. As part of a well-balanced diet, Pureharvest Aussie Dream helps provide a tasty nutritious food. It is totally lactose-free and can be used on cereal or in cooking as a dairy-free substitute.

All Natural

At Pureharvest we pride ourselves on using only natural ingredients, free from artificial additives and pesticides.

Taste & Nutrition In Pureharvest Organic Aussie Dream Rice Milks, we believe we have created the best tasting yet natural rice milks available.

- Unsweetened

- No Cane Sugar

- Gluten-Free

- Cholesterol-Free

- Lactose-Free

- Non-Dairy Product

- Suitable For Vegetarians

- No Preservatives

- No Pesticides

- No Herbicides

- Say No to Genetically Altered Products Please visit our website!
